STEP 1: Move project (IMPORTANT)
Your current path has spaces:
E:\projects\BSp

STEP 2: Open terminal in NEW location
Open CMD or PowerShell in:
E:\projects\bsp-dashboard
  
STEP 3: Delete old installs (MANDATORY)
Run these commands exactly:
rmdir /s /q node_modules
del package-lock.json
  
STEP 4: Install dependencies again
npm install

STEP 5: Install Vite correctly (THIS IS THE KEY STEP)
npm install --save-dev vite @vitejs/plugin-react
  
STEP 6: Verify Vite EXISTS
Run:
npx vite --version
  
 STEP 8: Start project
npm run dev
